<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>PART</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>叹酸菜鱼，一个人也能吃 &lt;&lt;</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201119/34feabb9a84047debab438f76c054a7e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Ⅱ金汤熬足2小时，酸辣开胃Ⅱ</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/24aecb9a0e364363acc9e3e86236f413.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201119/dbfd08bc29d2469ca4a0860274035ce3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">单说这一份酸菜鱼，金汤要<strong>熬足2小时</strong>才能上桌，喝起来<strong>酸辣开胃，让人食欲大开</strong>~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Ⅱ满满一碗黑鱼片，唆着吃Ⅱ</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/1d3851f3f8b4421d92ba2ccc65534917.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『72街』酸菜鱼选用的是黑鱼，相比市面上常见的草鱼、鲢鱼，<strong>肉质更为紧实，嫩中带脆而且鱼刺很少</strong>，嗦起来十分爽滑~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201119/67b17006d1664a28b1d8669db1f67d90.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>●●●</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201119/9d77265ada8d445791ba1c93c8e67cc8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">酸菜鱼看着份量不大，其实放满了肉肉~而且块块都<strong>又大又厚实</strong>，饭量小的仙女想要吃完可得努力！真实良心食堂没错了~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Ⅱ酸爽配菜，仙女连干两碗饭Ⅱ</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201119/cb63c87495d54af0b09008bcc5eca0ac.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201119/26af7acf97474e4bbbcb5a410decb8bb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201119/b8a969062ca74d2c835b9285cd4a3b6c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201119/9fac562c795b487a976d47b9feb7be4f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">酸菜鱼不仅鱼肉多，配菜也hin丰富~<strong>老坛酸菜、金针菇、木耳</strong>都配齐了，<strong>加汤捞一碗白米饭</strong>，好吃得说吃不下了的仙女都<strong>连干两碗</strong>~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Ⅱ小吃甜品一起上Ⅱ</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201119/6c65d63c1438454bb083461101022ca7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201119/5e4757de77864bc88a9351da41731c36.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">担心酸菜鱼太辣的朋友可以<strong>随心搭配小吃和甜品</strong>哟，小编选择了蒸蛋和红豆沙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201119/262631e4a2514aa6ac5a5b1ff76f1049.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这个蒸蛋必须要夸一夸~不加过多调味品的蒸蛋<strong>滑嫩清淡</strong>，轻轻一捞就会<strong>DuangDuang抖臀</strong>，不是布丁胜过布丁~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>PART</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201119/fac29362d7d34b0da3b04599b1920fda.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">火遍大江南北的<strong>国民美食黄焖鸡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Ⅱ120 天走地麻鸡，够鸡味！Ⅱ</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201119/19fe418e54f84096a4432f3620db9d2b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201119/d25553c584884b17bfb2f7165f7d7d8d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『72街』选用<strong>放养足120天的清远走地鸡</strong>，<strong>原产地直供</strong>，每一只都经过<strong>严格选拔</strong>，鸡界创造101走出来的鸡才够鲜嫩~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Ⅱ块块鸡腿肉，皮脆肉嫩Ⅱ</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/3bad5573e072490a8185613bb78d15a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">黄焖鸡配菜极少，香菇、青椒用来提味，碗里真的<strong>都是肉肉肉肉肉</strong>···而且被切成了小块，不仅<strong>易夹易嚼，还更加入味</strong>~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201119/193cad9b494c4f89a301bb09a7c7fcc4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/20edbb9b21f24bf89c9244567429d7b5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">差点忘了！黄焖鸡的<strong>酱汁采用十三种秘制酱料调制而成</strong>，无味精、无原料添加剂，鲜香扑鼻，用来捞饭仙女还可以再吃亿碗！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Ⅱ晚餐这样搭，绝不会错Ⅱ</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201119/9af9199d29c1434d84ea243aa556ce3b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">小编给黄焖鸡搭配了<strong>新品炒米粉和菜干龙骨汤</strong>出道~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/358ef6eb9ff347098b02558584783e97.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>炒米粉</strong>专为晚下班的打工人准备~炒米粉<strong>少油少调味</strong>，鸡蛋+胡萝卜丝+洋葱的搭配健康又轻脂，<strong>入口顺滑不噎喉</strong>，嗦就对了~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201119/a410da7d7dd94f26b5d1d9b3749a4e64.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>菜干龙骨汤</strong>原盅出炉，连味精都不加，<strong>原汁原味</strong>，煲汤水平一流的阿嫲都赞~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>03</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>PART</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>下楼就能吃 &lt;&lt;</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Ⅱ明档自选，一周7天不重样Ⅱ</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201119/6565af979daa4709ae8fcc765309e840.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201119/fc92f257da7d4701b5097cc898603e76.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201119/57b1e04d497146eb986cf3450912d87f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201119/e279180448b3411bb614a2a89d00e931.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『72街』不用多说，一直来都因为<strong>优质的食材、丰富的菜品、贴心的服务</strong>被广州街坊力挺~3<strong>0+菜品明档自选</strong>，一周7天不重样是小case~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Ⅱ饭菜现做，街坊邻居都放心Ⅱ</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201119/c2ab8db8003e48999357dbdd2ebdbc2f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201119/eab7027f5e454259b9df6df0a2833be9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">● ● ●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201119/e5f179bac5684a5b871f2cbc5fcb0339.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">『72街』的菜品<strong>根据客人取餐情况现做</strong>，保证大家吃到的都是刚出锅的新鲜好味~<strong>实惠，菜品美味，环境洁净</strong>，难怪从早到晚都有街坊排队~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201119/1beb119069994d128b43fb577cdea3e1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">工作再辛苦，也别忘了要好好吃饭哟~</p>
