<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201119/1461703577f243a4b2e10a34c26c82e7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201119/447f2cd2bfa4465f89779803a83f55c9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201119/5904ae348cba4c9f881e6312b45f972a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201119/660c090ab9024ec4858f6cee257df784.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201119/0b6ccc20e3d64b5fba35655a11799434.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201119/4605cbba0399473b8507e1a99ae0d014.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201119/c3227f67c26b4d079741cb338e054738.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201119/53a6a36a386142f1bfb7f7eaf11e4b08.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201119/898c2dafa66a422abd0965de98dfa3c4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201119/dd18858d5c774bf29240264d77432ab6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">贤合庄主打<strong>蒸笼热卤火锅</strong>，进门就是两口大锅，<strong>23味香料慢卤12小时</strong>！<strong>明档热卤，现点现捞</strong>，路过都看得心痒痒…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201119/7aefbc134fbf42f08951074108ac6ee1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">✌✌<strong>✌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/98915919a6f84f268d54f4a98bb1ce20.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店里还有一辆小推车铛铛<strong>敲着锣叫卖</strong>，充满了市井气息。主打<strong>9款热卤</strong>，可以直接吃也可以下锅涮，<strong>边卤边烫新吃法</strong>，也就贤哥想得出来！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>这三道卤菜，都爱到不行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>陈赤赤心头好 · 一碗牛杂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201119/d4a93ea21e204fd7bf3035729ac867bc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">老板陈赤赤都爱了，上桌必点好吗！猪杂很多，牛杂却不常见。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/821cccd583b14b579a0b249652bc79e7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201119/83881b16433e4bdca3793228f7068206.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">卤得恰到好处的<strong>牛心、牛肚、牛肠、牛舌</strong>，还有吸饱肉汁的白萝卜和笋干… 不管浇上卤汁吃还是放进锅里涮一涮，都超过瘾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>叶一茜爱吃的 · 牛蹄筋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201119/5428bb4813354db2bb3e128c7a723713.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">没有女孩子能逃得过<strong>牛蹄筋</strong>！经过12小时卤煮，卤汁渗进牛蹄筋里，后劲十足，就连森蝶麻麻也沦陷了~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201119/64abb73c066743edb997d9a30432f022.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">软软糯糯，带着<strong>满满胶原蛋白</strong>，直接吃或放进红油辣锅沸一回，都是四个字：入！口！即！化！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>朱桢爱吃的 · 手剪香菇肥肠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201119/496b4e97ebe34c66b3fbc2a7be43bb66.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201119/3be4f557a49b43ae8ee7802e4ad62316.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">肥肠处理得很干净，和香菇一起卤过之后，<strong>香而不腻，还会在嘴里biu汁！</strong>很多不吃肥肠的朋友，到了贤合庄就<strong>“真香”</strong>了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201119/1c9f3ac86c264f7d825ea9c3c66f4f57.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201119/e68a22060c2e47efa90826b46e6fa540.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201119/646cdf404f9e4baea2790ae4fa968f6e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201119/70e9bcb2233e46dab68d6923fc489687.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有卤豆干，卤鹌鹑蛋，统统卤得香喷喷，一口气倒进锅里涮上30秒再吃…<strong>鲜辣爽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201119/e1c32a2d12634b34a73ed47f34b94c51.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201119/e8142844deb34c79bcd1073a75f9a67a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">除了卤物，贤合庄还有<strong>60+种涮菜可选</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201119/6be83e5d53904053a896814b8eef5dea.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201119/b5a8691ebd3543babc0247585bbc78b9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>卤汁+秘制牛杂锅底</strong>，连牛油都是陈赫的招牌手势！沸开后的红锅香气扑面而来，忍不了了！开涮！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>= 火锅「三巨头」必须有=</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201119/2544655c1f09413ba3f286ec07b0f4ab.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201119/869af54bb22f4ff099014df110eb6fe9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
