<p class="ql-align-justify">贤合庄一贯走的是老成都<strong>复古潮流风</strong>，既怀旧又时尚。你熟悉的原木条凳、复古格纹桌面…都在！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201119/e91fd26816a845f6be625222c80aba0c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201119/76c0f6bfa9d948f7aecffe64c8f77a24.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">随处可见的明星签名、锦旗、相框…好像<strong>大型追星现场</strong>！迷妹们来看看有没有自己爱豆的签名照~</p>
